OVERVIEW
*********
MENU BOOT WILL INSTALL A BOOT MENU ON THE BOOT OF YOUR DISKS AND BY PRESSING
THE FUNCTION KEYS F1 TO F10 WILL LOAD THE CORSPOUNDING PROGRAM FROM THE BOOT
INSTEAD OF FROM THE NORMAL STARTUP SEQUENCE.
BY PRESSING THE LEFT MOUSE BUTTON YOU CAN EXIT THE BOOT AND THE NORMAL DOS
STARTUP WILL TAKE PLACE.

